Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.18,0:00:07.27,Italics Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,A fireworks festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.77,0:00:10.52,Italics Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Going out with friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.53,0:00:13.27,Flashback Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,I'll invite Kariu to \Nthe fireworks festival...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.15,0:00:15.16,Flashback Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,...and confess!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.17,0:00:26.66,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,So, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.66,0:00:28.28,Italics Dialogue,Honoka,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.28,0:00:29.29,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.36,0:00:32.58,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,...gonna tell Oga how I feel today.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.84,0:00:37.62,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,Oga said he might go to college elsewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.62,0:00:41.93,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,And here I was taking it for granted\Nthat we'd be together in college, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.93,0:00:45.98,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,But if we end up separated, \NI'll regret not saying anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.54,0:00:50.27,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,So help make sure we're alone together!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.90,0:00:55.80,Italics Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,If you know you'll be separated...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.74,0:00:58.53,Italics Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,...then falling in love...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.20,0:01:00.03,Black Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.72,0:01:01.68,Italics Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,...or confessing your feelings...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.03,0:01:01.83,Black Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an6}Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.83,0:01:03.29,Black Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.52,0:01:05.57,Italics Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,...kind of seems pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.72,0:01:11.54,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Hishiro-san! Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.06,0:01:15.05,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.05,0:01:17.94,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,There is nothing worse \Na person can do than be late!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.94,0:01:19.73,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,This failure can never be forgiven.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.73,0:01:22.90,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody would ever say that to \Nsomeone three minutes late.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.90,0:01:24.64,Main Dialogue,Honoka,0000,0000,0000,,You okay, Hishiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.64,0:01:25.66,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.66,0:01:27.60,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,I've never been to a festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.60,0:01:30.48,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,I completely underestimated the crowd.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.48,0:01:33.28,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,I can't apologize enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.28,0:01:34.95,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Her first festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.94,0:01:38.53,Episode Title,,0000,0000,0000,,Confession
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.95,0:01:38.53,sign_2277_32_Frankfurters,,0000,0000,0000,,Frankfurters
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.95,0:01:38.53,sign_2277_33_Corn_on_the_cob,,0000,0000,0000,,Corn on the cob
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.95,0:01:38.53,sign_2277_34_Soba,,0000,0000,0000,,Soba
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.95,0:01:38.53,sign_2277_35_Cold,,0000,0000,0000,,Cold
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.42,0:01:38.30,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Well, everyone's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.54,0:01:41.03,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,And Hishiro-san's calmed down. Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.49,0:01:44.58,Main Dialogue,An,0000,0000,0000,,Arata-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.58,0:01:46.33,Main Dialogue,An,0000,0000,0000,,I'd love some takoyaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.33,0:01:47.25,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,So buy some.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.25,0:01:48.51,Main Dialogue,An,0000,0000,0000,,Meanie!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.51,0:01:50.00,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,You can afford takoyaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.00,0:01:53.04,Main Dialogue,Honoka,0000,0000,0000,,Aki-chan! Let's catch some goldfish again!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.04,0:01:54.46,Main Dialogue,Inukai,0000,0000,0000,,You're on.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.46,0:01:55.93,Main Dialogue,Asaji,0000,0000,0000,,Don't catch too many!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.93,0:01:58.17,Main Dialogue,Asaji,0000,0000,0000,,Remember last year? That poor stall owner.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.02,0:02:01.32,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,Man, it's hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.32,0:02:02.30,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.84,0:02:06.77,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,You okay, Hishiro-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.54,0:02:09.83,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,How far'd you run?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.83,0:02:11.60,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Your feet hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.60,0:02:13.74,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,My feet are fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.12,0:02:18.54,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,But the crowd's a bit much, \Nand I'm a little dizzy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.54,0:02:20.24,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.24,0:02:21.75,Main Dialogue,Need,0000,0000,0000,,Need an arm?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.87,0:02:26.50,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,See? Like them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.08,0:02:29.37,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Keeps you from tripping, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.88,0:02:33.21,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,You don't mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.21,0:02:35.31,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,I offered, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.28,0:02:40.18,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Then I will accept your offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.29,0:02:43.84,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Look, we need to be subtle.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.84,0:02:45.68,Main Dialogue,An,0000,0000,0000,,I know, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.68,0:02:48.36,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Gotta leave those two alone naturally—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.75,0:02:55.80,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.80,0:02:58.38,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Is Yoake-san really making\Na move on a high school girl?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.38,0:03:00.37,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, out of the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.31,0:03:04.99,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Ryo...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.14,0:03:08.22,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Yoake-san might not be...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.76,0:03:11.17,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,But could Hishiro-san be...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.96,0:03:18.89,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where is everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.89,0:03:20.61,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,Did we get separated?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.61,0:03:21.23,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.58,0:03:26.47,Italics Dialogue,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Enjoy your alone time!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.65,0:03:28.78,Italics Dialogue,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.87,0:03:30.57,Italics Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,Already?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.66,0:03:33.47,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, I asked for it,\Nbut this came out of nowhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.47,0:03:35.68,Italics Dialogue,Both,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not ready yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.56,0:03:41.29,Main Dialogue,Inukai,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Tama?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.29,0:03:43.98,Main Dialogue,Inukai,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up, or I'll catch them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.98,0:03:46.54,Main Dialogue,Honoka,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, no fair! I won't lose, though!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.54,0:03:47.42,Main Dialogue,Shop Keeper,0000,0000,0000,,You! From last year!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.42,0:03:48.62,Main Dialogue,Asaji,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.62,0:03:50.66,Main Dialogue Top,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Distance to target: 1 meter.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.94,0:03:51.70,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,It went well, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.66,0:03:53.72,Main Dialogue Top,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,If gravitation force is {\i1}g,{\i0} \Nand my throw is at 180 degrees,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.91,0:03:55.52,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, do something about An!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.72,0:03:55.52,Main Dialogue Top,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,I need a force of...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.52,0:03:57.22,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,She's being super clingy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.52,0:03:57.22,Main Dialogue Top,An,0000,0000,0000,,Will that math help?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.36,0:04:01.28,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm... it would be a problem \Nif we had a subject
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.28,0:04:04.72,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,and an employee hanging out, \Nignoring the students.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.72,0:04:07.94,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,But everyone's here today, so it's fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.94,0:04:08.56,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,You're lax!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.00,0:04:10.52,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.03,0:04:12.85,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,You aren't bothered by Onoya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.85,0:04:15.88,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,You don't like me being with Hishiro-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.85,0:04:18.50,Main Dialogue Top,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,10 cm diameter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.00,0:04:18.30,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.30,0:04:21.17,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,You should have said!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.50,0:04:20.32,Main Dialogue Top,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Pi is 3.14...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.32,0:04:21.88,Main Dialogue Top,An,0000,0000,0000,,Will those calculations really help?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.17,0:04:22.86,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I didn't even notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.88,0:04:22.86,Main Dialogue Top,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Quiet, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.86,0:04:23.74,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.74,0:04:25.50,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,It's the last summer of high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.88,0:04:29.95,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,It's a precious time that won't come again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.95,0:04:32.17,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,But I guess for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.17,0:04:34.83,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,this is your first and last summer!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.17,0:04:37.25,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,You... god damn sadist!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.80,0:04:40.73,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,So what am I supposed to do about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.48,0:04:47.13,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,Can't wait for the fireworks!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.36,0:04:55.90,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Kariu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.90,0:04:58.28,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,I, uh... love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.76,0:05:11.78,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,Out of the blue?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.78,0:05:14.26,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,With all these people around?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.26,0:05:16.09,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,Not good timing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.26,0:05:19.28,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,Not exactly, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.28,0:05:21.17,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,But that's not the point...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.76,0:05:22.85,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.85,0:05:24.56,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody told me this would happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.56,0:05:26.70,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think he'd do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.70,0:05:28.17,Italics Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think you'd do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.50,0:05:33.85,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,Are you... serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.85,0:05:36.11,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,What? You don't trust me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.11,0:05:39.04,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,N-Not that! I just can't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.04,0:05:41.02,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,That's the same thing, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.20,0:05:43.35,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.86,0:05:47.01,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't mean it like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.86,0:05:51.06,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I came up with so many ideas.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.62,0:05:53.63,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't supposed to go like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.87,0:05:55.69,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,Kariu!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.92,0:05:57.57,Main Dialogue,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.08,0:06:09.38,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,When you asked me to these\Nfireworks, I was so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.90,0:06:12.37,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,Oga...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.37,0:06:15.65,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,I remembered you talking about \Ngoing to college elsewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.36,0:06:19.02,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,So I made up my mind to tell you today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.14,0:06:26.76,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,I've been in love with you \Nsince our first year, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.76,0:06:28.53,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,Will you go out with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.66,0:06:42.34,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! I summon all my courage to \Ntell you, and that's how you react?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.34,0:06:44.60,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, who wouldn't be surprised?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.60,0:06:47.43,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,I was gonna ask you out,\N but you asked me instead!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.43,0:06:49.48,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,Right back at you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.04,0:06:52.15,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.88,0:06:59.07,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.07,0:07:01.34,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,I... how should I put this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.34,0:07:05.69,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,I've never really talked about \Nthese things with friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.70,0:07:08.69,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'm not good \Nat picking up on things.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.82,0:07:13.23,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,I had no idea you felt that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.25,0:07:17.12,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't notice how I felt, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.70,0:07:20.78,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,Not until Arata gave me a push.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.78,0:07:23.29,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that without you, \Neverything would be so boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.77,0:07:28.46,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,The idea of someone else touching you...\N was just not okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.08,0:07:33.50,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,I only realized this recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.92,0:07:35.12,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,But I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.72,0:07:38.26,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,...I've loved you for a long time, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.89,0:07:46.20,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, man! That was really embarrassing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.20,0:07:49.06,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get embarrassed on a delay!\NYou're making me blush!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.48,0:07:52.48,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,Are these fireworks starting soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.48,0:07:53.62,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.14,0:07:58.04,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.50,0:08:00.33,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,Kariu-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.98,0:08:04.55,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,Do you mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.44,0:08:07.21,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,...if we hold hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.14,0:08:19.11,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,I... I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.03,0:08:24.08,Main Dialogue,An,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Asaji-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.08,0:08:25.79,Main Dialogue,An,0000,0000,0000,,You brought a sheet!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.79,0:08:27.11,Main Dialogue,Asaji,0000,0000,0000,,Sit down!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.70,0:08:28.96,Main Dialogue,Inukai,0000,0000,0000,,A mosquito just bit me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.96,0:08:31.32,Main Dialogue,Asaji,0000,0000,0000,,Here, medicine. Need some bug repellent?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.32,0:08:34.00,Main Dialogue,An,0000,0000,0000,,What? Asaji-kun, are you our mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.00,0:08:36.82,Main Dialogue,Honoka,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where are Kaizaki-san and Hishiro-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.82,0:08:39.33,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah... who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.33,0:08:42.66,Main Dialogue,Honoka,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... but the fireworks are starting!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.66,0:08:44.42,Main Dialogue,Inukai,0000,0000,0000,,Tama, you need bug spray?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.42,0:08:45.87,Main Dialogue,Honoka,0000,0000,0000,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.58,0:08:50.43,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where'd Yoake-kun and...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.44,0:08:55.17,Flashback Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,But I guess for you, this is \Nyour first and last summer!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.89,0:08:59.30,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,They set me up, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.02,0:09:05.63,Italics Dialogue,Announcer,0000,0000,0000,,Attention. Fireworks will begin soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.85,0:09:09.22,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Man, we're really boxed in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.85,0:09:13.19,Italics Dialogue,Announcer,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Please enjoy the beautiful fireworks \Nagainst the clear summer sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.68,0:09:12.57,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Hishiro-san, wanna just watch from here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.57,0:09:13.19,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.66,0:09:16.52,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Ryo...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.24,0:09:20.64,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Is he a friend of yours, Kaizaki-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.64,0:09:23.03,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen you talk at school, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.56,0:09:24.85,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.85,0:09:27.52,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we're friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.52,0:09:28.75,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.28,0:09:33.48,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Kaizaki-san, you make friends \Nwith everybody very easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.24,0:09:39.62,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,In April, you'd just enrolled,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.62,0:09:43.60,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,but you were already surrounded by friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.36,0:09:48.70,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,I remember seeing that and clearly thinking,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.70,0:09:50.64,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,"I've got to try harder."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.64,0:09:53.97,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Hishiro-san, you're here with everyone, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.97,0:09:55.42,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Seeing the fireworks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.42,0:09:57.08,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Except we got separated.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.76,0:10:00.88,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,You're surrounded by friends,\N too, Hishiro-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.63,0:10:03.08,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,You've tried plenty hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.03,0:10:07.41,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.21,0:10:10.26,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,The credit is mostly yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.72,0:10:16.79,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really glad I met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.52,0:10:36.04,Main Dialogue,An,0000,0000,0000,,Gorgeous!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.50,0:10:44.92,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,Beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.92,0:10:46.05,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.90,0:10:50.28,Italics Dialogue,Both,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm so focused on my left hand, \NI can barely watch the fireworks!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.90,0:10:50.28,Main Dialogue Top,Both,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I'm so focused on my right hand, \NI can barely watch the fireworks!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.62,0:11:04.30,Flashback Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really glad I met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.38,0:11:07.52,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,What did she mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.47,0:11:11.07,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, she meant nothing more.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.07,0:11:14.85,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,If she felt like it, Hishiro-san \Nwould totally say that to anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.28,0:11:17.98,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't mean anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.46,0:11:25.90,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.90,0:11:27.81,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,For thinking of me that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.54,0:11:29.52,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,That alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.82,0:11:34.01,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,...makes me think this ReLIFE \Nwas worth living.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.26,0:11:39.64,Italics Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Though you'll forget me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.64,0:11:41.09,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,They're lovely.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.60,0:11:49.08,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,But there's something a little sad\N about them, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.08,0:11:50.39,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,There is?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.96,0:11:56.52,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,They're so flashy, pretty, and exciting, \Nbut as they fade, you feel sort of lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.56,0:12:03.73,Flashback Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,You're an illusion that's meant to fade away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.48,0:12:13.17,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,When the experiment ends,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.03,0:12:15.93,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,so will this life.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.16,0:12:18.29,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,They'll forget me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.28,0:12:24.08,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Including Hishiro-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.40,0:12:29.66,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,They'll all forget me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.10,0:12:48.21,Flashback Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,They're so flashy, pretty, and exciting, \Nbut as they fade, you feel sort of lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.55,0:12:53.47,Flashback Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Hishiro-san, you're here with everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.47,0:12:54.59,Flashback Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Surrounded by friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.59,0:12:55.37,Flashback Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,You've tried plenty hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.37,0:12:56.98,Flashback Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad I met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.98,0:13:01.47,Flashback Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,If you know you'll be separated... \Nit kind of seems pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.47,0:13:02.77,Flashback Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,A confession?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.77,0:13:04.34,Flashback Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Ryo was in my class last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.34,0:13:05.40,Flashback Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,He told me to call him that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.40,0:13:06.90,Flashback Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,It's not often that you start a conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.90,0:13:09.39,Flashback Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Kariu-san and Tamarai-san \Ngave them to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.39,0:13:10.90,Flashback Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,It's not often that you start a conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.90,0:13:12.14,Flashback Dialogue,Both,0000,0000,0000,,It's all thanks to you, Hishiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.14,0:13:13.77,Flashback Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,I did that. I don't recommend it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.77,0:13:15.10,Flashback Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,They're all irreplaceable.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.10,0:13:16.68,Flashback Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,You can't turn back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.68,0:13:17.94,Flashback Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give up like I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.94,0:13:18.81,Flashback Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.81,0:13:19.44,Flashback Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Fight on!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.44,0:13:20.19,Flashback Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Together.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.19,0:13:21.57,Flashback Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,You're in my class?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.57,0:13:22.69,Flashback Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,I'm changing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.69,0:13:23.94,Flashback Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,You have more friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.94,0:13:26.86,Flashback Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,I forgive you. After all, we're friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.86,0:13:27.53,Flashback Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Can I have...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.53,0:13:28.53,Flashback Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,A friendly smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.53,0:13:29.28,Flashback Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,...your phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.28,0:13:32.45,Flashback Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Out in the real world...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.45,0:13:34.37,Flashback Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,That's my seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.00,0:13:37.33,Flashback Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.33,0:13:41.17,Flashback Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,You've been selected as the \NReLIFE Laboratory Kanto Branch's
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.17,0:13:43.63,Flashback Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,test subject no. 001!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.26,0:13:47.28,Flashback Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you, Hishiro Chizuru-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.73,0:13:57.31,Flashback Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,After the ReLIFE period ends,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.31,0:14:03.23,Flashback Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,classmates, teachers, and anyone\Nyou dealt with will forget about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.20,0:14:14.32,Italics Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,The more fun I have, \Nthe more it'll hurt when we part ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.32,0:14:16.87,Italics Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,I know that all too well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.93,0:14:20.24,Italics Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,I know this is a bad idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.67,0:14:28.13,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Kaizaki-san, you're like the fireworks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.76,0:14:30.59,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.30,0:14:34.68,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing, never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.19,0:14:39.84,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Hishiro-san, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.90,0:14:47.15,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Kaizaki-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.11,0:14:50.65,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,That face is really creepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.65,0:14:51.78,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.82,0:15:31.49,Main Dialogue,Honoka,0000,0000,0000,,That was so much fun! Oga-kun, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.95,0:15:34.28,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,No, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.33,0:15:37.75,Main Dialogue,Honoka,0000,0000,0000,,See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.25,0:15:44.92,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll walk Onoya-san home!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.92,0:15:47.30,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Take care of Hishiro-san, Arata!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.30,0:15:50.01,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,You live in the same direction, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.01,0:15:55.85,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,That's true. Kaizaki-san, do you mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.85,0:15:56.72,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.01,0:15:59.56,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Kazu-kun, look after Kariu-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.62,0:16:00.77,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.04,0:16:12.47,Flashback Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,You don't like me being with Hishiro-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.86,0:16:14.96,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.96,0:16:16.97,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,I just never see them together.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.97,0:16:18.61,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,It was surprising, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.10,0:16:21.11,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hishiro-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.45,0:16:23.62,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.62,0:16:26.18,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.18,0:16:28.50,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,The crowd got to me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.50,0:16:31.62,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Let's rest here a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.82,0:16:34.64,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.00,0:16:39.11,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really glad for Kariu-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.47,0:16:40.64,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,And Kazu-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.14,0:16:42.52,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.52,0:16:47.25,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is, Kariu-san was also \Ngoing to ask Kazu-kun out today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.59,0:16:51.68,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Because Kazu-kun might be \Ngoing to a different college.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.62,0:16:55.95,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,She said if that happened, \Nshe'd regret not saying anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.38,0:16:58.70,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, wow. Kariu, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.66,0:17:01.75,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,When I heard that,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.75,0:17:05.19,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that falling in love \Nwhen you knew you'd have to part
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.19,0:17:07.18,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,seemed pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.95,0:17:15.17,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,But when I saw them together, I was \Nhappy for them from the bottom of my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.68,0:17:18.06,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe worrying about future partings so much
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.06,0:17:24.23,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,that you miss out on happiness \Nin the present is a waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.83,0:17:31.98,Flashback Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone you dealt with\Nwill forget about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.98,0:17:33.01,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe so.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.92,0:17:40.27,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Someday, we'll part. Maybe be forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.17,0:17:45.04,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,But we're living in the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.34,0:17:47.03,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.32,0:18:00.84,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Hishiro-san, make lots of friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.84,0:18:02.13,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,fall madly in love,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.66,0:18:05.80,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,and enjoy every moment to the fullest.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.12,0:18:10.86,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I'll try.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.40,0:18:15.61,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,All I can do is cheer her on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.12,0:18:18.87,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,She'll forget all about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.87,0:18:21.74,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,If all her memories are about me,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.74,0:18:25.90,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,then she'll have no memories \Nof this year left.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.10,0:18:29.39,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,I'll vanish one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.07,0:18:33.49,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,I can't rob her of the life \Nshe's fighting so hard to have.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.70,0:18:36.99,Flashback Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,I was just wondering \Nif there's anyone you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.36,0:18:40.59,Flashback Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Someone you're always with.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.00,0:18:44.38,Flashback Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,You don't want anyone taking her away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.38,0:18:45.78,Flashback Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,You wanna hold hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.20,0:18:49.90,Flashback Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,You wanna kiss her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.96,0:18:51.90,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Kaizaki-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.62,0:18:58.46,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.46,0:19:04.11,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,You just find it cute that a high schooler's\Nawkwardly but earnestly trying to change, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.96,0:19:07.20,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Like watching a kid sister grow up?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.60,0:19:12.17,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Kaizaki-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.90,0:19:15.78,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Come to your senses!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.78,0:19:17.13,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Get it together!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.74,0:19:20.52,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Hishiro-san's life will go on,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.52,0:19:21.61,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,and I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.41,0:19:24.13,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,...won't be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.92,0:19:29.73,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.12,0:19:33.15,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.34,0:19:42.25,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.25,0:19:44.81,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I'd recovered.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.81,0:19:46.59,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't imagine I'd trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.16,0:20:11.53,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.53,0:20:12.68,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad I caught you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.09,0:20:20.53,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,You okay? Not gonna trip again?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.53,0:20:21.75,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.75,0:20:23.29,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,You sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.92,0:20:25.75,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,If you're that worried,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.98,0:20:30.02,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,then let me take your arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.24,0:20:33.58,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Ryo offered me his.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.18,0:20:41.04,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.04,0:20:42.88,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.09,0:20:48.32,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Someday we'll have to part.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.32,0:20:51.09,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,And I'll be forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.70,0:20:53.74,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.25,0:20:57.76,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,I won't ever forget you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.30,0:21:10.80,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I won't forget you, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.50,0:21:19.13,Main Dialogue,An,0000,0000,0000,,Kaizaki-san, you suck!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.13,0:21:21.71,Main Dialogue,An,0000,0000,0000,,Even though Senpai\N showed you how to link arms!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.71,0:21:24.84,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, that was your idea, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.84,0:21:26.76,Black Signs,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,ReLIFE Experiment Report
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.59,0:21:29.64,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I've got a good report \Nto write today.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.77,0:21:34.89,Main Dialogue,An,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.89,0:21:37.94,Main Dialogue,An,0000,0000,0000,,Kaizaki-san's the man I thought he was!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.94,0:21:42.19,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Yep. He managed to get Kariu-san \Nand Oga-kun together.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.19,0:21:43.83,Main Dialogue,An,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yeah, but he also...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.36,0:21:47.08,Main Dialogue,An,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.45,0:21:54.08,Main Dialogue,An,0000,0000,0000,,If she's with Kaizaki-san, \NHishiro-san, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.46,0:22:03.46,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's up to you. Since you'll be \Ntaking over as her support next term!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.46,0:22:05.09,Main Dialogue,An,0000,0000,0000,,Right! I'll do my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.77,0:22:18.02,Italics Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Kaizaki Arata causes change \Nin those around him.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.65,0:22:21.94,Italics Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,This is a direct result of his own actions,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.94,0:22:24.94,Italics Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,his drive to get involved \Nwith the people near him.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.94,0:22:30.82,Italics Dialogue,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,That, more than anything, \Nproves his ReLIFE is going well.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.27,0:23:01.11,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,Hishiro-san, what's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.77,0:23:04.14,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,I used the camera for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.57,0:23:06.15,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,It came out blurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.15,0:23:08.74,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,When did you take that?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.74,0:23:12.55,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Fireworks may vanish, but memories remain.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.08,0:23:15.83,Main Dialogue,Oga,0000,0000,0000,,Arata! Save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.25,0:23:17.50,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,"Save me"?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.50,0:23:19.21,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,What am I, some sort of demon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.21,0:23:21.79,Main Dialogue,Rena,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Hishiro! I won't lose this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.38,0:23:26.04,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0000,0000,0000,,Kaizaki-san... you're quite popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.05,0:23:29.30,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Is that what this looks like?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.84,0:23:32.97,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,A one-year, limited edition of youth.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.97,0:23:35.93,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,I may be an illusion that'll be forgotten...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.97,0:23:40.73,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,...but I'll treasure every moment, and enjoy...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.48,0:23:45.69,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0000,0000,0000,,...my ReLIFE!
